### Constructor

~~~ .xmp.php
Language();
~~~

Get language files from the `lot\language` folder then convert it into object:

~~~ .php
$language = new Language;
~~~

#### Set

~~~ .xmp.php
$language->foo = 'bar';
~~~

~~~ .xmp.php
Language::set('foo', 'bar');
~~~

